{"tid":2458068,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"京下旨解決貧窮  張建宗︰既得利益者須妥協","createTime":"2021-03-23T06:59:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T22:41:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"a69f3d675bf11148e6862c883ef6b87bdb610ecf","tid":2458068,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T06:59:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210323/U4VVUJT4IRFZ3A77YDCDS7X6NA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210323%2FU4VVUJT4IRFZ3A77YDCDS7X6NA%2F&d=9ZLePgUN12BIej1hBtk97Uxj1a1M9JfR6d2dSWReNkw%3D&h=f890e754\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210323%2FU4VVUJT4IRFZ3A77YDCDS7X6NA%2F&h=c4f8a335\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210323/U4VVUJT4IRFZ3A77YDCDS7X6NA/</a><br />\n<br />\n京下旨解決貧窮 <br />\n張建宗︰既得利益者須妥協<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/51ywcft5oDjlEeRMYCYPp45R_uw=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UTXUF72CRBEOTMZ3HCWGJTTJ24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F51ywcft5oDjlEeRMYCYPp45R_uw%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUTXUF72CRBEOTMZ3HCWGJTTJ24.jpg&h=6471d5e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n張建宗<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】國家副總理韓正月初在全國兩會時與港區人大代表會面，提出要解決香港住屋問題，政務司長張建宗接受英國《金融時報》訪問時稱，北京已指示港府解決住屋及貧窮問題，形容新環境下，一些既得利益者須妥協。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n揚言撤資公司必後悔<br />\n<br />\n林鄭早前接受鳳凰衞視訪問時已透露，獲中央支持處理房屋土地問題，張建宗在訪問中再指，<span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"large\">北京指示港府</span></span>將更多重點放在低收入人士，政府將努力解決住屋、土地及貧富差距等問題，但不涉加稅，形容新環境下，「一些既得利益可能要妥協」，似暗示要向地產商及地主「開刀」。<br />\n<br />\n對於早前有外資擔心香港實施港版國安法後法治受損，甚至有報道指外資撤離，張揚言撤資公司會後悔，並指他們將會重回香港，強調香港法官現時就職須作司法誓言，在北京眼中已「足夠」，也不會修改以普通法為基礎法制系統，指香港仍是「稅務天堂」，籲外國投資者不必擔心。<br />\n<br />\n而本月初曾在接受彭博訪問時指，北京出手「完善」香港選舉制度令政制發展「後退一步」的律政司長鄭若驊，昨於《文滙報》專訪「洗底」，大讚中央此舉對律政司工作「有幫助」。<br />\n<br />\n鄭指律政司人員作為「治港者」之一，除要愛國，亦要「do the right thing」，明言不會放下專業及對法律忠誠。<br />\n<br />\n另外，全國人大提出立會議席由70席增至90席，立會行管會昨早曾討論相關問題，據知已向秘書處提出研究擴建方案，如為召開大會會議廳及內會與財委會議室加設座位，議員辦公室地方不足問題也要研究。"},{"pid":"f115644e7ecd8afc2ac9d27e10b0cf1dc8587685","tid":2458068,"uid":25794,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T07:05:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />走資"},{"pid":"904a961d918e475104bb09c7baeb5b9bd359d58b","tid":2458068,"uid":16676,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T07:33:06.000Z","msg":"講清楚d 解放香港咪算囉<br />\n諗咁多籍口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當年解放上海咪又係氹住d 有錢佬唔好走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dc4a1b2dd0d8da11e3fa70d2ab8eab59c7cf17a","tid":2458068,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T07:38:01.000Z","msg":"曹總： 史無前例！歐美英加三十國制裁新疆酷吏！ 澳洲謀立法制裁追落後，張建宗驚到即晚改口重申港人治港<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2457757\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2457757</a>"},{"pid":"abbb81be90b573d3f1606b709c7a6896f238f738","tid":2458068,"uid":71748,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T07:38:46.000Z","msg":"丁權收皮了"},{"pid":"34635693ee69305f2e4a968766b2568585d7e4ef","tid":2458068,"uid":97970,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T07:39:03.000Z","msg":"公屋撚又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"805cb4a9ed1a450df90f3fbada2e1051149dcc13","tid":2458068,"uid":265485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T07:39:47.000Z","msg":"點解肥宗同林鄭依排講嘅野成日相反<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5de1c6afcfbf4554907b35e2a12b59639cb12255","tid":2458068,"uid":284855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T07:40:33.000Z","msg":"打土豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.g